@ Everyone!

To burn these files is simple and I only use one program and that is Nero..

If there's anyone else who uses another program to burn, please let others know..

With Nero it's simple:

Click on Nero burning rom - Choose DVD video - Click on "new" -  Choose ONLY, VIDEO_TS  and AUDIO_TS folders and drag them to the far left - Then all it is is "BURN"
